Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak, squeak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how the hamsters eat their food so squeaky clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're squeakily cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Welcome back.\NI was just shooting a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomba let me have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A single-lens camera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why would he give you something so COOL?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he bought a new one\Nso he won't use this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made by a different company,\Nso none of the lenses fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, I'm with Team Canon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds like Bomba...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, taking photos doesn't really sound like Bomba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been doing it since high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, he gets bored easily\Nand jumps from hobby to hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that DOES sound like Bomba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how about I snap off a shot\Nwhile you just act natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? H-hold on, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that acting natural?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna leave behind a memory of me,\NI may as well look good in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes it sound like I'm painting her friggin' portrait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! I'll take YOUR photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks kind of plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Big Brother! Give us a smile! Say chee...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I was making some kind of weird face, wasn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You friggin' took it when you'd only said "Chee"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos are a lot of fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, there are some old photos in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Bomba left the memory card in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Kirie looks so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's an old one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go looking at other people's photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this memory card back to Bomba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, finding old photos is kinda fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Big Brother! Let's take tons of pics!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're STILL taking photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take photos of the hamsters,\NI might be able to enter them in a contest again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei, I bought a new camera,\Nso I'll give you my old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna come by and get it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a single-lens, right?\NDon't you want to hold on to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanukichi will be all grown before you know it.\NShe won't be living with you forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take pictures of her now, while she's acting natural.\NYou'll thank yourself for it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, there's nothing more\Nto take pictures of in here. Let's go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we go for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna take a picture of, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The scenery, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a picture of you drinking cola\Nwith the setting sun in the background!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in even being outside for that, is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bomba, you left your memory card\Nin the camera you gave me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there any photos on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you only take one pic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with this crazy-ass face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th..they're closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But they can't! This is where you and I\Nhave made so many memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a travesty, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,TSF, it says they're closed for cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go? Nyaon would be crowded,\Nand we went to the candy store just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, UMR! There is somewhere that I wish to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This department store is totally retro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?! It is a nice old department store, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the story directory calls to mind a bygone age!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This escalator is SO nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even have a food court, just restaurants\Nwhere you have to buy a ticket for your order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And this staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the sign leading to the rooftop is wonderful, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,An arcade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like an amusement park, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That crane arm is SUPER strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Sylphin and I both grew fond of that nostalgic\Ndepartment store and started going there often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That department store, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We should go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I guess we should before it closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Closes"? It's going belly-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an old building\Nand there aren't many customers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? It's great\NBECAUSE it's old and there aren't many customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no way for the stores to stay open, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! I got "Excellent Luck"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As did I!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is a liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a single sign that says they're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, there aren't many customers,\Nbut it's still got some life left in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Places like this make you hope\Nthey stick around, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that even once you and I have become adults,\Nwe can reminisce and talk about "that time when."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we're talking, we can think to ourselves,\N"I'm glad we became friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,TSF...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't you worry. This is staying put.\NNothing's going to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that always a vacant lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right. That's a lot of empty land...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if some big building used to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be... an amusement park there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? An amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was most fun, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I first realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, UMR! There is somewhere that I wish to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin knew that the department store\Nwould be closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about we all go to the amusement park\Non our next day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to go, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I will go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This familiar scenery....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we become adults, it will have changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if the scenery changes,\Nthere are some things that will never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they exist in our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ebina. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um! I got some rice in the mail, from Akita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This year as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ebina. You should join us for dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure I don't eat too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I make today...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is new crop rice, right?\NI should make something extra tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do YOU always make, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if I'm using rice, kiritanpo hotpot, or...\Noh, oyaki dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, you're from Akita all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you need mochi rice for oyaki,\Nand kiritanpo takes a lot of time to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to make something in time for lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about takikomi rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drag you into the kitchen,\Nbut you'll be a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm in the kitchen with Taihei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-th-this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like what Kirie said before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina! I have a cunning plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A "plan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the way to a man's heart\Nis through his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His stomach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, through FOOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Feed Taihei some of your home cooking\Nand you'll land him for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,L-l-land him?! No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Land him! Land him! For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really concentrating hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that from being from a farming family?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, I'll help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a little cramped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let her cook alone with Big Brother,\Nshe'll find out HE'S the one who always makes the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to help out, at least a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, I'll trim the chicken and dice the vegetables.\NWould you mind rinsing the rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to cook the chicken,\Nso you can get the frypan ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be able to do that, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's too small. It's for frying eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I knew that! I was just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The larger one's down below there,\Nso go ahead and add some oil for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Must be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Land him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie... Sure enough, I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave Ebina such a shock that she fell!\NWhat if she'd hurt herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And why did you add that much oil\Njust for browning the chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I got a little confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Ebina. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I can't cook at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to grab him... but he grabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that little accident aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's for dinner tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday is bread day, so what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who I ran into on the way home.\NSo, I invited her over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ran into," you say? And where\Ndid this meeting take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it wrong for me to come, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That was a sneer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her PLAN to come here, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's got you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had dinner with us before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him as he was leaving the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so I called out "Big Brother!" and he replied "Hikari!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S NOT A COINCIDENCE AT ALL!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be outside of his office\Nand he just happened to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing coincidental about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's purely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought those two were friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got Umaru in such a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, maybe Hikari came over so they can get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't it bread day today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's bread day. So, let's make pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I think it's ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us making something together\Nwill probably help them break the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, who's up first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I shall make you the perfect pancake, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Perfect," huh? That's a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is pour this on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, I can make a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick is to wait until the surface starts to bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sorcery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Delish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun to make food together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you make more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, these are your two.\NYou said you made them for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, don't force yourself.\NThere's no way those will taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because I wanted to eat bread with you.\NIt wasn't a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot this last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty incredible that you got an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I GOT AN AWARD TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is for AP classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They recommended that I take AP classes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You're getting mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT GETTING MAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak. Hamjiro, Hamsaburo, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding-ding-ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, and the wild hamsters have appeared!\NLet's get your hamster ball ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Umaru! Don't treat your hamsters like toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you've got it all wrong, Big Brother.\NWe're just playing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're trying to play,\Nyour pets aren't having any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making the same face as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, small animals have been known to die from stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always in the same place, inside their cage.\NYou have to treat them with care, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And good afternoon, hamsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, are you not letting them out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. 'Cause Big Brother said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pet stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he thinks I tire them out\Nby playing with them too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a long time ago at an aquarium I went to,\NI heard that even fish can feel stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All those people coming and going\Nand standing there in front of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the hamsters always stay inside the house,\Nso I think they're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamjiro, Hamsaburo, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup, Tanukichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Hamjiro and Hamsaburo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru must be tough to put up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a bit selfish, but don't hold it against her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm back! Games, Internet, and anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamjiro, Hamsaburo, c'mon out! Let's have a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was the usual fun and games...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do next?\NStill, it's not like you can understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling any stress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Big Brother will be home soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Your hamster ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well! You two wanna play with me after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Today it's the Pokeham the Movie 2000!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! What? Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to play with your hamsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just us doing the preview again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time there were just WAY too many spoilers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here in the script,\N"It will be fine. She trusts Umaru."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, faith is the biggest,\Nmost irresponsible kicker of them all, huh?
